%% Diagram: Deduplication window state machine
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Unseen
    Unseen --> Seen: first report (SET NX EX 600)
    Seen --> Seen: duplicate within window (drop)
    Seen --> Expired: TTL elapses (10 min)
    Expired --> Seen: next report (SET NX EX 600)
    Expired --> [*]: key swept
